<L>__{interior parlour, black cove farm. day}
<A>__{from the window ada watches the cabriolet head towards town. at the piano, she unwraps the leather lace from the package of music. inside the first book of music, there's a daguerreotype of inman with his lemats, a typical confederate pose. some of the music has left its imprint on the picture, the notes like a melody over inman's face. ada picks them out on the piano. the ebullient sound of shape singing. a noisy choir letting rip }
